#: hosts_keeper/app_help.py:14
msgid "命令和参数"
msgstr "Commands & Arguments"

#: hosts_keeper/app_help.py:18
msgid "命令"
msgstr "Commands"

#: hosts_keeper/app_help.py:22
msgid ""
"要执行的操作，可选值为：\n"
" - [u]list[/]：列出所有配置文件。\n"
" - [u]show[/]：显示当前配置文件的内容。\n"
" - [u]edit[/]：编辑当前配置文件。\n"
" - [u]update[/]：按照所有激活的配置文件更新hosts。\n"
" - [u]help[/]：显示帮助信息。"
msgstr "Operation to perform. Options:\n"
" - [u]list[/]: List all profiles.\n"
" - [u]show[/]: Show current profile content.\n"
" - [u]edit[/]: Edit the current profile.\n"
" - [u]update[/]: Update hosts with all active profiles.\n"
" - [u]help[/]: Show help."

#: hosts_keeper/app_help.py:33
msgid "配置文件ID"
msgstr "Profile ID"

#: hosts_keeper/app_help.py:36
msgid "配置文件的ID，在 show 和 edit 命令中必须要指定。"
msgstr "The profile ID, required for the show and edit commands."

#: hosts_keeper/app_help.py:42 hosts_keeper/appcontext.py:111
msgid "搜索模式"
msgstr "Search Pattern"

#: hosts_keeper/app_help.py:46
msgid ""
"如果在 list 中指定了搜索模式，将只会显示符合条件的配置文件。搜索模式支持 glob "
"形式的通配符，并会智能搜索配置文件的多种信息以找到符合条件的目标。"
msgstr "If a search pattern is specified with list, only matching profiles will be shown. The search pattern supports glob wildcards and searches multiple profile fields."

#: hosts_keeper/app_help.py:54
msgid "目标文件"
msgstr "Target File"

#: hosts_keeper/app_help.py:57
msgid "指定目标 hosts 文件，默认值为系统 hosts 文件。"
msgstr "Specify the target hosts file; defaults to the system hosts file."

