msgid "跳过刷新"
msgstr "Skip Flush"

#: hosts_keeper/app_help.py:63
msgid "更新 hosts 后跳过 DNS 缓存刷新，仅输出平台对应的手动命令提示。"
msgstr "Skip DNS cache flush after updating hosts; only output platform-specific manual command hints."

