#: hosts_keeper/app_help.py:82
msgid "建议通过完整帮助信息学习更多使用技巧。"
msgstr "Learn more usage tips from the full help information."

#: hosts_keeper/app_help.py:87
msgid ""
"本工具通过一系列配置文件自动编写操作系统的 hosts 文件。\n"
"        配置文件可通过 [u]list[/] [u]show[/] [u]edit[/] 等命令进行管理。\n"
"        执行 [u]update[/] 命令后，hosts 文件将被自动更新。\n"
"        当然，编辑 hosts 文件需要以管理员权限运行。"
msgstr "This tool manages the system hosts file through a set of profiles.\n"
"        Profiles can be managed via [u]list[/], [u]show[/], [u]edit[/].\n"
"        After executing [u]update[/], the hosts file will be updated automatically.\n"
"        Editing the hosts file requires administrator privileges."

