msgstr "Options for controlling transcoding operations"

#: media_killer/mk_help_info.py:18
msgid "指定（多个）需要处理的文件，包括[u]预设文件[/]和[u]源文件路径[/]。"
msgstr "Specify file(s) to process, including [u]preset files[/] and [u]source file paths[/]."

#: media_killer/mk_help_info.py:24
msgid "指定目标文件夹，如果不指定则默认为当前工作目录。"
msgstr "Specify the output folder; defaults to the current working directory."

#: media_killer/mk_help_info.py:30
msgid ""
"设置任务的排序模式，在执行任务之前将会按照指定的模式进行排序。\n"
"            "
"四种模式分别为[u]按源文件路径排序[/]、[u]按预设排序[/]、[u]按目标文件路径排序[/]、[u]按输入顺序排序[/]。"
msgstr "Set the task sorting mode. Tasks will be sorted before execution.\n"
"            The four modes are: [u]by source file path[/], [u]by preset[/], [u]by target file path[/], [u]by input order[/]."

#: media_killer/mk_help_info.py:40
msgid ""
"\n"
"                设置并行工作进程的数量，默认为 1 。\n"
"                不建议设置大于 2 的数值，除非你知道你在干什么。\n"
"                "
msgstr "\n"
"                Set the number of parallel worker processes. Default is 1.\n"
"                Setting a value greater than 2 is not recommended unless you know what you are doing.\n"
"                "

#: media_killer/mk_help_info.py:50
msgid "启用[red bold]强制覆盖模式[/]后，将忽略配置文件中定义的覆盖选项。"
msgstr "When [red bold]force overwrite mode[/] is enabled, overwrite options in presets are ignored."

#: media_killer/mk_help_info.py:55
msgid "启用[green bold]安全模式[/]之后，将忽略一切覆盖选项，无论如何也不会覆盖目标文件。"
msgstr "When [green bold]safe mode[/] is enabled, all overwrite options are ignored; target files will never be overwritten."

