msgstr "Generate a sample preset file. [uu]Sample file cannot be run directly![/]"

#: media_killer/mk_help_info.py:70
msgid "保存转码任务为脚本文件，将不再主动进行转码操作。"
msgstr "Save transcoding tasks to a script file; will not perform actual transcoding."

#: media_killer/mk_help_info.py:75
msgid ""
"加载上次的[u]所有[/]转码任务并重新执行。\n"
"如果想要继续运行未完成的任务，建议附加 -n 选项。"
msgstr "Load [u]all[/] transcoding tasks from the last run and re-execute.\n"
"To continue running incomplete tasks, append the -n option."

#: media_killer/mk_help_info.py:93
msgid ""
"本工具从用户提供的输入中识别[u]预设文件[/]和[u]媒体源文件[/]，\n"
"            并基于它们生成一系列任务，并调用 FFmpeg 进行转码。"
msgstr "This tool identifies [u]preset files[/] and [u]media source files[/] from input,\n"
"            and generates tasks to transcode via FFmpeg."

